title: Prince Harry and Meghan to Be Honored at Project Healthy Mind’s World Mental Health Day Festival
summary: The couple and Archewell Foundation co-founders will be feted as humanitarians at the Oct. 9 gala and, the next day, will appear as their foundation is co-producing a series of discussions at the fest.

summary: The unravelling of two companies deemed weeks ago to be in strong health sparks concern
